snippet: The French Open quarter-final between holder Serena Williams and Yulia Putintseva resumed following a 15-minute rain break on Court Philippe Chatrier on day 12 of the championships on Thursday....
lead_paragraph: The French Open quarter-final between holder Serena Williams and Yulia Putintseva resumed following a 15-minute rain break on Court Philippe Chatrier on day 12 of the championships on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Serena Resumes Quarter-Final at French Open After Rain Break
